==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''[[sex]] [[on]] [[a]] [[stick]]'''

#{{slang}} A person (or people) who is (or are) considered very sexually attractive.
#:''She thinks David Beckham is sex on a stick.''

====Synonyms====
*[[sex on legs]]

